Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: date
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Responsible for logging date of an event. Example “2020-10-02 17:44:37 +0000”.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: libraryName
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Responsible for logging name of this library. Can be used to filter logs in the console.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: emoji
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Emoji character used distinguish failure from success.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: statusCode
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: HTTP status code of a given request. Only logged for NetworkingPluginEvent.responseError and NetworkingPluginEvent.success.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: httpMethod
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: HTTP method used for a given service.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: headers
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Headers used for the request. Only logged for NetworkingPluginEvent.dataRequested.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: data
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Data associated with a request. For NetworkingPluginEvent.dataRequested this is the body of the request. For NetworkingPluginEvent.responseError and NetworkingPluginEvent.success it’s the data that was returned from request. For NetworkingPluginEvent.unableToParseRequest this is not logged.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.name: Element
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin/Element.h.abstract: Enum that gives NetworkingLoggerPlugin information on what user wants to log.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin.html#/s:2.name: init(elements:)
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin.html#/s:2.abstract: Initializes the plugin with information on what the user wants to log to console.

Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin.html.name: NetworkingLoggerPlugin
Structs/NetworkingLoggerPlugin.html.abstract: Plugin that logs information about service requests being made.
